  <Summary>Troy Little&#8217;s gonzo adaptation of Hunter Thompson&#8217;s Fear &amp; Loathing in Las Vegas is now available in an all-new format. Find out why GQ said &#8220;Little&#8217;s cartoonish sensibilities make him the ideal artist to adapt Thompson&#8217;s gonzo ur-text... perfectly portraying literature&#8217;s most ridiculous road trip.&#8221;

This comic book version is presented in black-and-white and at a slightly larger size than the full-color hardcover edition. Each issue also includes pages from Little&#8217;s sketchbook and other behind-the-scenes information.

